  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_133",
    "english": "Among the orcs of the Demon Realm, these kinds have completely settled in the human world, doing tough work for a living. The executor is a tough job doing all kinds of work, but for an orc that started at rock bottom, it is one of the professional jobs. From finding people to collecting debts, they would even line up in front of a popular store if told to.",
